snippet.textDisplay: It is in odia language- one of the 6 classical languages of India . Bande utkal janani is the national song of odisha. It was used as a odia sign of patriotism during odia nationalism period . Rangabati is the popular folk song from paschim odisha. Odissi music and folk dances like chhau dance is too popular , odissi dance is too a classical one are from Odisha .If u want to know more info, please search on internet or try Wikipedia ....With love and Thanks for appreciating the song.
